headline: Nvidia earnings, SCOTUS tariff fallout, geopolitical tensions rise: What to watch this week
summary: In the upcoming week, investor attention will focus on fallout from the Supreme Court's tariff ruling, tensions in Iran, and Nvidia's fourth quarter earnings.

headline: Is Keurig Dr. Pepper Inc. (KDP) One of the Best Sugar Stocks to Buy According to Hedge Funds?
